Try to put some logic on your work and save time.

title: 820-3478  No power
message:
Post U6921 voltages.
Also check L7410/510 for voltage.

title: 820-3478  No power
message:
L7410/510 voltage must appear before CPU core.
In fact L7510 and CPU core voltage cannot appear without L7410 voltage.
So check U7400 basic voltages: pins 13, 14, 3.
